              perfect condition.
              <i style="color: var(--color-primary-dark);" class="fa fa-quote-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-inner-col">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <img src="/img/faces/p2.jpeg" alt="">
            <div class="testimonials-inner-name">Elizabeth D.</div>
            <div class="testimonials-inner-stars">
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              <i class="far fa-star"></i>
              <i class="far fa-star"></i>
            </div>
            <p>
              <i style="color: var(--color-primary-dark);" class="fa fa-quote-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              I received my order today and I am very impressed with the quality! Thanks for doing an outstanding job! I
              will not hesitate to recommend or use your services in the future!
              <i style="color: var(--color-primary-dark);" class="fa fa-quote-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-inner-col">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <img src="/img/faces/p3.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="testimonials-inner-name">Bill More</div>
            <div class="testimonials-inner-stars">
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              <i class="far fa-star"></i>
            </div>
            <p>
              <i style="color: var(--color-primary-dark);" class="fa fa-quote-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              My order was received in a timely manner, even though, due to the coronavirus, deliveries have been
              disrupted. I am very please with my purchase.
              <i style="color: var(--color-primary-dark);" class="fa fa-quote-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%- include('../includes/end.ejs') %>